## 6. Running Tests

```bash
# All tests
pytest

# With coverage
pytest --cov=app --cov=pipelines --cov-report=html

# Unit tests only
pytest tests/unit/

# Specific test file
pytest tests/unit/test_lead_time.py

# Specific test
pytest tests/unit/test_lead_time.py::TestLeadTime::test_calculate_lead_time_simple

# Verbose with print output
pytest -v -s
```

