## 7. Coverage Requirements

| Module | Minimum Coverage |
|--------|-----------------|
| `app/services/` | 80% |
| `pipelines/assets/` | 80% |
| `app/api/` | 70% |
| Overall | 75% |

### Exclude from Coverage
```ini
# pyproject.toml or .coveragerc
[tool.coverage.run]
omit = [
    "tests/*",
    "*/migrations/*",
    "*/__init__.py",
]
```

