## 8. Security Practices

### Secrets Management

```bash
# .env (gitignored)
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=secure_password_here
JIRA_API_TOKEN=secret_token
JWT_SECRET=32_char_minimum_secret_key_here
```

### Secret Requirements
| Secret | Min Length |
|--------|-----------|
| Database password | 16 chars |
| API tokens | 24 chars |
| JWT secret | 32 chars |

### Generate Secure Secrets
```bash
# Python
python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(32))"

# OpenSSL
openssl rand -hex 32
```

