## 11. Linting Configuration

```toml
# pyproject.toml

[tool.ruff]
line-length = 88
select = [
    "E",   # pycodestyle errors
    "F",   # pyflakes
    "W",   # pycodestyle warnings
    "I",   # isort
    "B",   # flake8-bugbear
    "S",   # flake8-bandit (security)
]
ignore = [
    "S101",  # assert usage (OK in tests)
]

[tool.black]
line-length = 88
target-version = ["py311"]
```

### Running Linters
```bash
# Check
ruff check app/ pipelines/
black --check app/ pipelines/

# Fix
ruff check --fix app/ pipelines/
black app/ pipelines/
```

